<!-- Game Controls Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S 100 METER CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Press just before the finish line to assume the finishing pose:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S LONG JUMP CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Select jump angle and landing:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S POLE VAULT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Pole release / Clear the bar:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / Square button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + X Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S HAMMER THROW CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Throw direction and angle setting:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / Square button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn (increase power) / After-throw grunt:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S JAVELIN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Throw direction and angle setting:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / Square button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn (increase power) / After-throw grunt:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S CLEAN AND JERK CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Clean / raise barbell overhead:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Increase power / Keep balance:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">WOMEN'S SPRINGBOARD CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Jump / Enter the water:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate diver:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">WOMEN'S 50 METER FREESTYLE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Finishing pose (press before finish):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Swim:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S 1KM TIME TRIAL CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Finishing pose (press before finish):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pedal:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MEN'S SPRINT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Change lanes:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pedal:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">SINGLES 500 METER CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Right stroke:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Left stroke:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle + Square Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">WOMEN'S HORSE VAULT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Jump from the springboard / Put hands on vaulting horse:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle / X button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Mid-air techniques:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle, X, Triangle, Square Button</font><br><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>

      
