<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Play as Konami man and Konami woman -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On the Select Event screen choose the event you want and press Up, Up, Down, Down, Left, Right, Left, Right, Circle, X.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Blimp on 100m -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">To get a Blimp to appear you must get the last 2 digits matching e.g. 10.33s or 8.77s.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Mole in long jump -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When doing the long jump, if you are lucky enough to get all three of the distances matching e.g. 7.77m or 8.88m. A mole will pop up from the sand.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Spacecraft -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When doing the Javelin throw, run real fast but throw at an awful angle (~70°). If you got it right you'll hit a spacecraft.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

